Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 你许了什么愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:23.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,保密！
