Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.36,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.24,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,保密！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:36.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,上啊 抚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:37.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,击溃他！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.35,Default,Group,0,0,0,,{\an8}击溃他！
