Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这咋回事啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你没事吧？！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.08,0:02:29.83,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\bord0.6\pos(1181,178)}第{\fs103}5{\fs}话   会被削成骨头的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这些肯定是刚刚那些小东西干的 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:37.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那些导弹一样的东西 击中了我们好多次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不是看着像啊 就是导弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:46.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有那些迷你迷你士兵邦邦地射得又疼又痒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定是那个吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,人小所以威力也小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:51.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也不懂 大概吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说回来 这玩意要怎么解开…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}是啊 你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:58.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊——真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.35,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,你们到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.89,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,先把这个解开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.70,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 你解开了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.59,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,那你到死都被绑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们来自吾野！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.82,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.84,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野的人也没变化吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也？你说「也」是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:36.84,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,我在问吾野的人是不是和之前一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然我们还没变 但之后会变成动物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.21,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,你们来这里有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来散步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们是来找医生的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你说出来干嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不能说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我打算一点点告诉他的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎样啦 我又不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一口气说出来的话 就没法讨价还价了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？我不是说了解开这个之后再告诉他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就是因为这样大叔都准备要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从一开始你那个态度就不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,大叔气到我了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也对这种大叔很生气啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.37,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,转起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么什么什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.23,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的脸！好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:18.99,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.90,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,你们很吵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.88,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,现在是我在问你们问题啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.44,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,自顾自吵什么架啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.29,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,而且与其说吵架更像是在讲我坏话！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,他突然好生气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.49,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,才没生气啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.13,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,谁会因为小姑娘生气啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.32,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,我可是队长啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.03,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,为什么队长要对小姑娘——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.50,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.94,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,我知道的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.60,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,要找医生的话 在吾野也能找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们在找一个叫医生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.82,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,为什么要博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:49.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,朋友长了蘑菇又拔了出来于是可能马上要死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.73,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,蘑菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.62,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,那个也是7G的影响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那肯定啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是肯定的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:56.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,绝对是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.39,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,果然 和老大说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,刚刚开始怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.76,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,立刻去进行报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,都告诉你了就快帮我们解开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.02,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,我可没作过这种约定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:09.92,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,不能让城市的消息泄漏给外部人员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.57,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,因为这是我们贤明的老大规定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:14.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,老大？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.65,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,根据老大的指示 明天你们的骨头将展示在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.93,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,狭山市立博物館的曙光剑齿象标本旁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,骨头是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,变成骨头的话我们会死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不就是死刑吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等啊混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,放开我 你们这群小臭虫！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:32.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,电流 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,电压 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}抚子！安东尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,来这里嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好——稍微等我一会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 晶在叫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,快点过来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:43.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}好好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:44.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,正常！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.41,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实和静留去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,晶一个人好无聊噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.53,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她们肯定很快就回来了 能不能再稍微等一会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:59.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,她们肯定偷偷拐去吃冷食了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:02.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所以我要和安东尼玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.33,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 在我点检完成前 她就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,安东尼你软乎乎好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.68,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,脸也越来越有弹性了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是的 手腕好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别弄了 会流血的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,手环要断开了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听听我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:24.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白医生确实在这个城市里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,之后剩下的就是去找了 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:30.90,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那把这个解开的方法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个还没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.03,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里才是最重要的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就不该对你有期待的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是的 就没有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等一下啊 姐姐你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,求你了 解开这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们来这里不是想加害你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们只是来找那个医生救我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:58.84,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,和你们说话的话 老大会削出我的骨头挂去展出的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以说这个老大是谁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.59,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,说出来的话会被削成骨头的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那你干什么还要接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,肯定有理由的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.75,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我负责打扫这里 是来找垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.29,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,如果有垃圾的话 会被削成骨头的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:13.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们帮你一起清理垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要在这里小便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从刚刚开始就没上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我忍不住了 所以要在这里小便！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然这样会把公园弄脏 不过也没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也要小便！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,会尿很多出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,之后就不关我事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要是你就这么放着我们不管的话 绝对会被老大干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留的吾野柔术真的很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也总之就是很厉害的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是帮了我们再被削成骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还是因为小便而被削成骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:46.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 稍微漏了点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,谢谢你 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.09,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:53.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们会去把老大干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.71,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但先带我们去见医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.20,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,博士被老大抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？假的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.92,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,得先救出知道博士在哪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,一个人都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.53,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,毕竟颁布了外出限制令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那么医生是为什么被抓起来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.35,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我按时间顺序讲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.84,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我们发生变化的原因 恐怕就是传闻中的7G事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:22.19,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,整座城先是持续膨胀 然后又因为反作用而变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.39,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,在这种情况下 有人把居民团结在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:28.67,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,那就是博士\N加波·诚·埃斯特朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好厉害！不管是事迹还是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.82,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,居民们以诚老师为领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.48,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,一同维持着除去体型之外一切正常的生活水平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.58,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,但就在这时 老大出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.01,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,老大只用了一瞬间就支配了城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:46.15,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,他抓住了居民的领袖诚老师 并监禁到了某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,老大有这么超级强吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.00,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,于是稻荷山的居民就此被分为对老大忠诚的上等市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:55.81,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,以及被剥夺了自由的下等市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.43,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我们下等市民的一切都被管理着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.94,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,为了设施的运作而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,设施 和孑孓差不多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.86,annotation,,0,0,0,,读音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.71,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我们被强迫 为了这座城镇的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.41,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,以及满足老大兴趣而供电
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不是很过分吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.65,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,大家都放弃抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.52,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,但是如果诚老师回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.91,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我们也许能再一次站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以你才会到我们那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:19.62,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:45.72,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.05,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,告诉我们诚老师在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.46,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,作为原上等市民的你肯定知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我绝对不会透露情报源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.18,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在在稻荷山公园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,正在找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.08,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,为什么要找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.71,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,有人生病了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:06.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,咦？不是告诉过你晶身上长了蘑菇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.19,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,蘑菇的事我听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.34,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,医生什么的我可不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你不是说稻荷山有医生的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:12.91,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.85,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那才不是帽帽帽帽帽帽帽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子你遇到麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的表情有那么明显吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,实际上 晶也有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,身体越来越重 手都慢慢动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是不用担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:32.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,遇到麻烦的话 不管什么时候玲实都会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的肚子好疼啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.36,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我也想不到你真会吃下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我课本没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是你自己吃干净的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,和晶你绝交了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.54,Flashback,Boy A,0,0,0,,喂 你看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.55,Flashback,Boy B,0,0,0,,呜哇 没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.62,Flashback,Boy B,0,0,0,,全都是字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我觉得很有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.01,Flashback,Boy C,0,0,0,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:54.34,Flashback,Boy C,0,0,0,,你是不是因为我们西吾野在秩父线上就嘲笑我们啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.29,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.64,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你们对晶做了什么啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是她今天稍～微有点迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:06.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等她回来之后一定要狠狠说教 哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:08.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也一起说教吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,请这样做吧
Comment: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.53,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs90\fnArial Black\c&H838A83&\fry10\pos(682.5,331.5)}J{\c&H89928A&}A{\c&H8F9B90&}S{\c&H95A496&}D{\c&H9BAC9D&}F
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.53,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord6\fnComic Sans MS\c&H323C2F&\3c&H748589&\fry10\pos(750,753)}本大爷的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.54,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,诚老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:47.89,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,山田 这是什么情况？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,稍后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.90,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们是来救你的 快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:03.14,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,你们俩 在本大爷的基地里想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不对 也就一般大小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.14,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,你们是怎么逃脱的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我才不说呢 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.29,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,再敢像这样胡作非为试试！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:13.03,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,看我不把你的头扯下来 再把你千刀万剐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,胡作非为的人是你才对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:15.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,他们都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.46,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,不是 太近了 你怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我正奇怪着为什么大家都服从你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,原来只是因为你长得比较大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.85,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,说得跟你很懂似的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:26.42,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,本大爷最讨厌的人\N就是你这种明明很蠢却自以为是的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也超讨厌你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.80,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,不对 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.87,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,我这边才是 更 更 更讨厌你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.21,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,喂 愣着做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.56,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,快开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.43,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.07,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这种力度也就能给我挠痒痒罢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,欧啦—！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.36,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,发射麻醉导弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我躲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.99,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这种攻击可不会对我生效第二遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.83,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,啊！我懂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.61,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,你们是想拉拢博士 然后把这里据为己有对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.42,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,我绝不会让你得逞！你这蠢辣妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:55.44,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 干得漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:02.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们赶紧回晶那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:03.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.08,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,别发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.72,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,快对博士开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.30,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,开火开火开火开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欧耶—！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.60,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,别放走他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.36,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,开火 开火 开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,可动人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶 这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是医生还有稻荷山公园的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等她治好了晶 我们就马上去救静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留…发生了什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.75,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我把医生带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.83,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,等等 我可不是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可你不是医生吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.20,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我是科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那不就完蛋了嘛！治不好她！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.02,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,总之先跟我说说来龙去脉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是医生就没有意义了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.58,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不久之前 我们把她屁股上长的蘑菇拔掉后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她就跟变了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.27,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,身体也渐渐变得无法行动自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.37,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.60,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,晶君？可以这么称呼你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.92,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇被拔掉之后\N除了身体感到沉重以外 还有其他变化吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,唔 让我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,脑袋里凉凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.29,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,你们运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.45,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,医生可治不好7G造成的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那老师您能治好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.11,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.06,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,即使是科学家 研究的专业也各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.67,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,但以我研究7G的进展 做出一些推测还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.09,Default,Group,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.71,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,老师您是研究7G的…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.02,Default,Man,0,0,0,,那老大之所以要抓走博士是为了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:33.32,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,他似乎知道我的来历\N并认为我有办法让这座城市恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:38.27,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我们把现在发生的事情称为「7G脑浪现象」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,七…十一…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:45.46,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,在7G的影响下 人的身体\N会随着意识的状态发生巨大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.97,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,想要变回原样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}请说得更简单易懂一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:50.30,DefaultOverlap,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是说 晶君的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:54.20,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,是源自某种重要的东西\N随蘑菇一起被拔出去了的认知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.59,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,那么为了让她认为那些东西能重回原位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.05,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,只要让她吃下蘑菇就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:58.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.90,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,就是蘑菇 你们手里有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.03,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,难道我们又得去东吾野一趟吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:06.62,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,不 我记得老大的房间里好像长着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,蘑菇吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.63,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果善治郎还活着\N说不定就能有更像样一点的对策了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么？你说善治郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:16.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你说的是吾野的平善治郎先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.59,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,你们怎么会…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.08,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,他还活着吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他还活着…只是脑子不太好使了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.20,Default,Nadeko,0,0,0,,善治郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.78,Flashback,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喵喵 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.15,Flashback,Surgeon,0,0,0,,喵喵手术 即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.60,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.39,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,别停下！快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.82,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,跑快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.47,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.42,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,总之 现在先解决晶君的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:06.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里是…哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.22,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,这是本大爷的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把我处决之后做成骨骼标本摆出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.29,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,也 也对 这么做好像也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:17.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,既然能自由活动身体 我可不觉得我会输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.10,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,啊 对 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你为什么要做这种事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这不就只是在欺凌弱小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.45,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,因为我…喜欢基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.39,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,不觉得很帅气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.60,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,战斗机 直升机 还有各种车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.01,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,我一直都很憧憬这些东西 只是没告诉过任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.91,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,但是 后来我好不容易交到了几个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.59,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,我就跟他们说 我想在这样的基地里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.42,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,然后我就被他们狠狠地嘲笑了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:47.55,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,他们说 以我的头脑和运动神经\N我的这个梦想绝对不可能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.36,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,然后 7G过后 我就来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.20,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,你一定会觉得这很无聊 或者觉得我疯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.22,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.89,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,为什么你要露出这样的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:06.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋…你去过池袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:06.60,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.18,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,你要去池袋吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.67,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,那里很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.42,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,与其那么冒险 不如和我一起留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.42,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,好？好不？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.87,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,顺便一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.80,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,如果你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.88,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,我就会放过你的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,把静留和蘑菇交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.68,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,所以我讨厌你这种辣妹啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,差不多也该住手了 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.44,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,住口！住口！住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:39.29,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,该死的巨大辣妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.76,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,我绝不会把我的基地交给你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,课本的事…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.59,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,命中目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.14,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.46,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,那样下去不妙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实 有些不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对那个家伙来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.59,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.72,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,诶？喂喂喂喂喂喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.75,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,你们这些笨蛋！救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.21,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我又搞砸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好难吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.79,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我不要再吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.77,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,没用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.51,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样下去的话晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样才不是晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:22.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你就应该脾气别扭 一天到晚都读这种难懂的书才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.11,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这本书是什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是你最爱的东西吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}吃下去！晶！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.25,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,最爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}等等等一下 玲实？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.65,DefaultOverlap,Makoto,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:34.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.78,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,说不定这样能行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是那个时候的回礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.55,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你都干了些什么啊 笨蛋玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.69,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.05,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是Sadist吗你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:46.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,Sadi…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:47.46,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,虐待狂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,即是说过激性欲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,通过给予他人身体上的虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.33,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,或者全身性的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,以获得性兴奋的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不懂的话去读读萨德侯爵的书！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嘛 对于笨蛋来说估计是天书了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊啊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我的龙彦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样一来我就只剩一本了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,而且那个是保存用的不能读啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.28,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.66,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你松手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:16.76,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\an8}放我下来！放我下来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个要去那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.24,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,被7G变得离谱地大的狭山湖里有一个无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.34,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\an8}放我下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.33,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,扔那儿的话基本就逃不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:25.22,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\an8}我不要去那种不毛之地啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.65,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我要去善治郎那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.42,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,去找出改善现状的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:34.79,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,我们成立了自警团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对啊 你们有武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,博士和我们是背道而驰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:41.07,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,以我们的体型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.25,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,即使给车装上手头全部的燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.35,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,也不知道要花多少天才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要小心啊 路上什么都有可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然对我们来说也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.50,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,前往目的地的旅途就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:55.08,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,正因如此 迈出第一步的勇气才最珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,手环 我会再给你做一个的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的？！
